Privacy Policy for Buzzer - An Interactive Quiz Soundboard

Effective Date: 8th September 2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to Buzzer - An Interactive Quiz Soundboard! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application ("App"). We understand the importance of your privacy, and we are committed to protecting it.

2. Information We Don't Collect

We want to make it clear that our App does not collect any personal information from you. We do not gather, store, or share any data that can be used to personally identify you or your device. The App is designed to be a simple and secure tool for quiz enthusiasts, and we respect your privacy.

3. Information We Collect

As mentioned, we do not collect any personal information. However, the App may collect anonymous usage data for the purpose of improving the user experience and fixing bugs. This data is entirely non-identifiable and includes generic information about the App's performance, such as crash reports and feature usage.

4. Third-Party Services

Our App does not integrate with any third-party services or social media platforms that would require the sharing of personal information.

5. Security

We take data security seriously. Despite not collecting personal information, we use industry-standard security measures to protect the App and its users from unauthorized access or data breaches.

6. Children's Privacy

Our App is intended for general audiences and is suitable for use by individuals of all ages, including children. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe that we may have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us, and we will take appropriate measures to delete the information promptly.

7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App. Your continued use of the App after the changes are made will indicate your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at calidaddeveloper@gmail.com.

By using Buzzer - An Interactive Quiz Soundboard, you acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
